Title: groupFinderWelcome
Content:
Let's get you in a group.
We are so excited for you to try this. It's new. Which can be scary. But trust us. It will be awesome.

Title: groupFinderSummary
Content:
Brave Groups

BRAVE groups meet once a week for 5 weeks, starting the week of April 3rd and ending the week of May 1st. Most groups take less than 90 minutes from start to finish.

Title: groupFinderParticipantExpectations
Content:
Let the grouping begin!

We’re gonna ask you 5 questions to help us connect you with the perfect traveling companions.

And then...

We’ll present you with several groups to choose from that will share similar goals, interests or wants. Doesn't that sound cool?? Great! Let’s roll.

Title: groupFinderHostExpectations
Content:
Look at you stepping up and leading the charge!

Thanks for being awesome. Now comes the part where we help you plant the seeds that will grow a super group.

Title: groupFinderHostConfirmation
Content: YO! This action is final, your information cannot be edited past this point.

Title: groupFinderHostPublishSuccess
Content:
You did it! You're group is now a real thing.

Have we said that we think you're awesome? Thank you for stepping up to host! A confirmation email is headed to your inbox.

We've also created a dashboard for you with everything you'll need to make your group a success. You can invite people to your group, you can contact group members after they sign up, and you can access all your materials. Check it out!!

Title: groupFinderParticipantUpsell
Content:
Are you sure you don't want to lead a group?

So we may have mentioned this. But we really really need leaders. And based on your answers we think you could be a great one. Last time we'll ask.

Sorry!

Title: groupFinderParticipantAnywhereConfirmation
Content:
Awesome! We noticed that you're a little off the grid.

Lucky you. This means you get even more personal service. Sit tight, someone from Crossroads will contact you shortly to facilitate your group.

You're in!

A confirmation email is headed your way that has all the details of your group. You can expect to hear from your host shortly.

Thanks for being BRAVE! You're going to love the group dynamic.

Title: groupFinderHostPrivateGroup
Content:
You're now the proud host of a private group!


Thanks for stepping up... But now you have to go the extra mile. it's time to head to your dashboard to let those invites fly.

We've created a dashboard for you with everything you'll need to make your group a success. You can invite people to your group, you can contact group members after they sign up, and you can access all your materials. Check it out!!
